      "part_type": "Hadith",
      "path": "/books/man-la-yahduruhu-al-faqih:1:16:8",
      "source_url": "https://thaqalayn.net/hadith/34/1/16/144",
      "text": [
        " «لاَ وُضُوءَ عَلَيْهِ مَا دَامَ قَاعِداً إِنْ لَمْ يَنْفَرِجْ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.144 - Imam Musa ibn Jafar Al-Kadhim (as) was asked about a man who falls asleep while sitting: does he need to perform ablution?\nImam (as) said: 'He does not need to perform ablution as long as he remains seated and does not slump over.'."
        ]
      }
    },
